# Customer UI Patterns

Customer UI should feel:
- modern
- minimal
- smooth
- visually appealing
- easy to scan

Use:
- clear visual hierarchy
- strong CTA buttons
- modern cards
- clean spacing
- readable typography

Prefer:
- responsive grids
- package cards
- lightweight transitions
- simple filtering
- minimal steps

Avoid:
- dashboard-heavy interfaces
- enterprise-style complexity
- cluttered tables for customers
- excessive text blocks

Focus on:
- discoverability
- fast actions
- easy checkout
- trust
- simplicity

Pages should load fast even on slow internet connections.
